PrecisAcceptance of an Instrument (DESIGNATION AND REVOCATION OF SURRENDER) wherein the SKEETCHESTN BAND surrenders, for a term of 15 years, some 1,053 acres of land on Skeetchestn Indian Reserve No. 0 in British Columbia, for agricultural and ancillary purposes, and revokes the surrenders it made in the years 1905, 1908 (two), 1922 and 1969.
